                    <h2 class="mt-2">Overview</h2>
                    <p>As UX/UI capability lead, I spearheaded the creation of our DXC UX process to help streamline how we work and developed best practices for the team to build upon. Evangelize the UX process both internally and externally to gain awareness and secure billable projects for the team.</p>
