                <div class="col-lg-8 mb-0 mb-lg-2">
                    <h2>UX Definition</h2>
                    <p>We visually design digital experiences based on a deep understanding of the users and the strategic business objectives. We validate these designs through usability testing and iterate based on user feedback.</p>
                </div>

                    <div class="col-lg-10 mb-0 mb-lg-3">
