                    <div class="col-lg-8 mb-0 mb-lg-2 mt-4">
                        <h2>DXC UX Process</h2>
                        <p>DISCOVERY - We start our process with principle lead discovery session using design thinking methods. The initial phase of our process of Discovery, we focus on understanding the needs of the users. We also aid in the defining of the problem.</p>
                        <p>DESIGN – We quickly move into rapid wireframing. We then solution based on the pain points discovered and present many variations of wireframes to the client and development team. We get approvals on high fidelity wireframes from the client before handoff to development.</p>
                        <p>DEVELOP, DEPLOY & SCALE – We then build out our ideas.We expand, service and test. We assist development in asset creation and oversee the design. We also use this time to test with our personas.</p>
                    </div>

